description: So this is what happens when we go to the library? ha! We pick up someone who thinks their dominant? See I'm here & handcuffed to this Saint Andrew's Cross with Brandie Mae & we're just wondering if Melanie Brooks can really be dominant enough, she really has no idea what I'm looking for. Brandie though, thinks we should give her a chance... let's see, I'm not impressed very easily & Brandie is hard to please. But I'm going to take Brandie's recommendation & give this Melanie a try, Brandie says she has spunk! Ok here she comes, sit back all & let's see how domineering Melanie can be! By the looks of it she has a chance... you be the judge!
title: Alura Jenson in Threesome Domination, or Not?
